ActYukon First Nations Self-Government Act
SubjectFinancial Transfer Agreements with Eleven Self-Governing Yukon First Nations
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to enter into renewed FINANCIAL TRANSFER AGREEMENTS with eleven Self-Governing Yukon First Nations in order to support Self-Governing Indigenous Governments in continuing to deliver programs and services to their citizens and implement their respective modern treaty and/or self-government arrangements.
